::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica smiles at Desmonus' words, walking off toward the room 
again, his arm around her along with Bloodystrike's arm. Both bots 
were excited in anticipation, trying not to act desperate.

"Would you preffer and empty room?" Reptilica asks Desmonus, 
realizing it was a stupid question as soon as it left his lips.




--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@h...> wrote:
> 
> * Desmonus watches as Reptilica turns and looks at her, simply 
stepping a 
> bit closer to him as he steps a bit closer, not minding at all at 
his 
> attempts to put his arm around her.
> But knowing that Bloodstraike was also trying to do the same thing.
> 
> She simply hissed a bit.
> Let them believe that I give a nano about them, she thought. Let 
them think 
> that they can get away with trying to extract pleasures from me. 
Not even 
> knowing that all I'm here for now is for a meal. But I can play 
their little 
> games, let them think they have the upper hand.
> As long as I can feed without threat of the supply running 
it ...all is 
> well.
> But she smiled at Bloodystrikes words and leaned towards him just a 
little.*
> 
> " Hmm...yes, a good idea indeed. Lead on, Reptilica."
> 
> * And with that she simply follwed the males, her stomach growling 
in 
> anticipation all the way.*
